
NAME 
    suck-site
     
DESCRIPTION
    Suck a remote website's files locally.
    
    This function requires two parameters...
        @1 = Directory to download site files to
        @2 = Remote URL

SYNOPSIS
    suck-site [DIRECTORY] [URL]
     
EXAMPLES
    suck-site /home/user/new-site http://remote-site.com
     
AVAILABLE OPTIONS:
    N/A
    
    
